<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">magazine</ENAMEX> has made the same choice). <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Clinton</ENAMEX> told the famous story of <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Roosevelt</ENAMEX>,
