second-class, temperament. He can't control his impulses, especially the
libidinal ones; he has an unattractive tendency to blame other <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">people</ENAMEX> for his
problems; he has a terrifyingly effective gift for misleading and,
occasionally, telling outright lies. <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">People</ENAMEX> who work for him rarely come away
