<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1998</TIMEX>.

            But though <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Clinton</ENAMEX> lacks a first-class temperament, he possesses a
first-class mind. By this, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Chatterbox</ENAMEX> doesn't mean only that <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Clinton</ENAMEX> is
knowledgeable and smart; <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Jimmy Carter</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Richard Nixon</ENAMEX> were knowledgeable and
